computer.booted
computer.failed
computer.snapshot.created
computer.paused
computer.resumed
artifact.created
policy.denied
budget.exceeded

Use JetStream for durable streams and replay. NATS JetStream persists messages and supports replay to consumers, which makes it a good fit for this event log.  ￼

