Must show:
	•	state
	•	CPU/memory/disk
	•	current task
	•	snapshot lineage
	•	nested services status
	•	latest screenshot
	•	logs tail
	•	open ports
	•	capabilities
	•	buttons: pause, snapshot, fork, stop

Replay page

Show:
	•	iteration timeline
	•	prompts used
	•	capability calls
	•	commands
	•	diffs
	•	screenshots
	•	verifier outputs

This replay/debugger is one of the strongest differentiators.

