Developer experience

Local dev mode

Support a no-K3s local mode with Docker Compose for control-plane services:
	•	postgres
	•	temporal
	•	nats
	•	valkey
	•	minio
	•	litellm
	•	frontend
	•	backend services

Then support one local Firecracker worker host process.

Commands
	•	make dev-up
