⸻

Final opinionated stack summary

Control plane
	•	Go
	•	gRPC + REST
	•	PostgreSQL
	•	Temporal
	•	NATS JetStream
	•	Valkey
	•	MinIO

Runtime
	•	Linux + KVM
	•	Firecracker microVMs
	•	containerd
	•	optional gVisor for nested untrusted containers
	•	guest Ubuntu images

Agents
	•	LiteLLM gateway
	•	vLLM for hosted OSS models
	•	Ollama for laptop/local mode
	•	Python for agent workers
	•	Go for orchestration

UI
	•	Next.js
	•	TypeScript
	•	Tailwind
	•	xterm.js
	•	Monaco

Verification
	•	shell
	•	HTTP
	•	Playwright
	•	screenshots
	•	diff reports

Observability
	•	OpenTelemetry
	•	Prometheus
	•	Grafana
	•	Loki

This is the stack I would choose if the goal is: serious open-source self-hosted VirtualPC, not a toy demo, and no AWS dependency.

